{
  "stem": "1518.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have the-- the power to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, nobody knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even the villages, or the group-- nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just soldiers from the Russian army that escaped the labor camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no Jews there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say at least six, seven months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we crossed, they took everybody into the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By [POLISH], when we met with the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not far from Dubno, about 40 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took everybody into the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want to take me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- the-- the commander and the guys says, he used to help us a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think you should-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] I think-- I think you should take him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyways, they took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we marched from 4 o'clock in the morning from [POLISH] to Dubno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was such a snowstorm, you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- even the horses couldn't get through with the sleighs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came to Dubno, they took everybody's name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they asked me where I was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time it was Poland, so they sent me into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to go to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to go to the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't matter to me, as long as-- as long-- as long as I went in, because all I wanted was revenge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from Dubno they-- they sent us to Sumy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was about 300 kilometers east of Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the-- no no, that was-- that was the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like they sent us into Sumy with Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when the Polish army formed, in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
